The New VW Caddy Life
New player in the compact van class
Up to seven seats and two sliding doors

The new Caddy Life combines good sense and lifestyle in attractive  
forms. As a representative of the compact van class, it reflects  
automobile traditions. The new Caddy Life additionally embodies  
contemporary lifestyle. It is an automobile for everyone - and for  
every event. It is a small VW bus.
